{"tid":871421,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人20幾歲第一次叫雞先知自己好細碌？","createTime":"2018-10-22T02:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T03:20:48.000Z","uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"47c883efa5e37c9494def5d086ce875f24c62d24","tid":871421,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"我咁大個仔除左睇AV未見過其他男性楊具，但Av打左格仔睇唔到男優條j實際有幾大<br />\n我以為自己都算中等jj size<br />\n<br />\n但早排第一次滴起心肝叫雞<br />\n沖完涼出黎準備破處啦。。。<br />\n我一條撚放落隻雞個口就知奶野，我扯硬左可以成條放晒入去佢個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢含左我一陣我覺得尷尬就話插啦唔含啦<br />\n上套果陣先柒，個套我根本帶唔實<br />\n隻雞幫我帶果陣只係劣左半個套落我碌野度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我都頂硬上唔撚理照插啦，一擺碌野去條女個西度就發現佢塊西仲大過我碌鳩<br />\n果下真係灰到軟左<br />\n最後叫隻雞幫我打飛機算，唔想搞<br />\n點知佢研究左一陣用👌🏻手勢套住我碌野黎chok<br />\n果刻我推開隻雞背住佢喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉屌我勸各位手足j細唔好叫雞"},{"pid":"1031ab56533b4b59ecebb6075f4f00ec4b610082","tid":871421,"uid":126690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4094ed5be1f0ce8d1d3468ed4ccf8865865bcd8e","tid":871421,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1031ab56533b4b59ecebb6075f4f00ec4b610082","tid":871421,"uid":126690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"真人真事，講假既我死全家"},{"pid":"0d97e6e586b0bb0c9be9b87ac4b772d90c4c10ac","tid":871421,"uid":191019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"唔好喊啦"},{"pid":"3f77a2bae802073a67f0fd0d7f4f77da73b3e1a9","tid":871421,"uid":126690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb5558fff9c504bbb67acf213f2ed